{"tid":585416,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突破】 可口可樂打破百年傳統 將在日本推酒精飲品","createTime":"2018-03-08T15:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T09:22:15.000Z","uid":28366,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ec59c1956c58d7f72ce50a70874d1a06776741c5","tid":585416,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/08/233554_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F08%2F233554_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7d002866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國可口可樂公司正計劃打破自身125年來的傳統，準備首度推出含酒精的飲品。他們想搭上在日本漸受歡迎的Chu-Hai氣泡酒熱潮，在當地販賣類似的罐裝氣泡甜酒。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司（BBC）7日引述可口可樂日本分公司總裁加杜尼奧（Jorge Garduno）表示，這項行動是「針對我們市場一小塊特定族群的小型試驗」。<br />\n<br />\n加杜尼奧還說：「我們從未在酒精含量低的飲料市場進行試驗。這將證明我們如何在核心業務之外領域持續開發機會。」然而他暗示，這款飲品很可能不會在日本以外地區銷售。<br />\n<br />\nChu-Hai是日本燒酎高球（highball）調酒的縮寫。這款產品被宣傳為啤酒的替代品，並且格外受女性消費者喜愛。日本3大飲品公司麒麟控股公司、三得利控股公司和朝日集團控股公司都已推出不同款的Chu-Hai氣泡酒，並持續研發新口味。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180308/57918225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180308%2F57918225&d=8jSl%2F07Erb5WLRU5GsSSW%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=49d3a77f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180308%2F57918225&h=edff7375\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180308/57918225</a>"},{"pid":"cdd3ec091bc323da8970a295633f21773c445cb3","tid":585416,"uid":46965,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:37:20.000Z","msg":"coke + vodka"},{"pid":"98ac9ee4b0bf3afeebc54f6373f7741f5b69b7e8","tid":585416,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdd3ec091bc323da8970a295633f21773c445cb3","tid":585416,"uid":